              "coded_information": [
                "GELI",
                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 7-cm3 Ge(Li) detector in connection with",
                "a multichannel analyzer, end-window proportional",
                "counter."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After bombardment the targets were",
                "taken to the chemistry laboratory. The chemical yield",
                "for each sample was determined after counting using",
                "atomic absorption spectroscopy. The decay rates for",
                "the 57Ni, 196mAu, and 196gAu were determined using a",
                "Ge(Li) detector. The decay rates of the 64Cu",
                "were determined by counting the beta radiations with",
                "a proportional counter."
              ]
            }
          ],
