                "value": 0.999
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The nickel targets were",
                "fabricated by electroplating isotopically enriched",
                " (99.9%) 58Ni to a surface density of about 5 mg cm-2",
                "onto 0.08-mm thick gold foil. During the irradiation",
                "all targets were flanked by a set of 99.9% pure",
                "aluminum foils: two 0.04-mm-thick inner guard foils,",
                "two 0.08- mm-thick beam-monitor foils, and two",
                "0.04-mm-thick outer guard foils."
              ]
            }
